}

###modificar autoridad (PUT - idempotente, modificaciones completas)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/10101013
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lautaro FERNANDEZ",
  "rank": "3",
  "zoneId": "1"
}


###modificar autoridad (PATCH - no necesariamente idempotente, modificaciones parciales)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/10101013
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rank":"2"
}

###borrar una autoridad
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/10101015
